erage probability), and\nvariance of the CSP are derived. Numerical results validate the analytical\nresults. Insights are extracted related to the reliability, coverage\nprobability, and latency of the considered network.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 28 May 2019 18:01:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 30 May 2019 13:18:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2019 21:13:06 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 7 Dec 2019 13:59:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-10"}
